&lt;DIV&gt;Each group with 1 tank, 2 clerics, 3 dps classes (or anyone really). This sound about right. Will be a miss match of gear levels depending on who I can bribe/beg/force into helping me.&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;Oh and if I can get this together and kill him what would I need to add to do the GF bards?? - thats if anyone will go near the place with all the nasty elves around.&lt;/DIV&gt;</description>
